If the dragon {{monsym|red_dragon}} is a pet flying over water, then displacing it will likely prove fatal for our hero, who has no place to step back onto dry land.  The more pets there are, the more confusing the situation is, and the more dangerous.  Do not try to navigate [[Juiblex's swamp]] with a swarm of pet [[Killer bee|bees]].
